events.name: Postgres New Year Meetup!
events.description:
The PostgreSQL v9.5 Beta2 is already out. Hope some of you have got chance to get your hands dirty with new features! Hopefully we will have the new release before the Christmas...Let's meetup in the new year to discuss on this new release. Also the Postgres community is planning to host an event in Singapore along with FOSSASIA (yey!). Let's discuss about that too  


Hope to see all of you there!

events.name: New Years Elixir Toasts
events.description: Let's start the new year with a sip of fresh Elixir goodness. Share your Elixir experiences from last year and what you'd like to see this year. What's your New Year's Elixir Resolution? :) Topics and talk proposals are very welcome for any level of knowledge. Cheers! Agenda 19:00 Start – grab some food and enjoy a drink with others19:20 Talk (30min)19:50 Break20:00 Talk (30min)20:30 Break20:40 Talk / Fishbowl (20min)21:00 End Food and drinks will be served.

events.name: Emotional Design -  The Foundation
events.description: A workshop for the foundation of Emotional Design .  Agenda: • 15min: Networking • 30min: Mini-talk on Emotional Design • 5min: Challenge review. • 30min: In pair, learn to identify Emotional Design components from a selected product. • 20min: Discussion. • 5min: Wrapping up.
events.location: Rakuten Crimson House, 138 Market Street, Lvl 32, CapitaGreen, 048946, Singapore
